  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n中支那方面軍司令官兼上海派遣軍司令官、ハルピン特務機関長、陸軍大将、Ａ級戦犯"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"07m.html\">一覧　（マ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E6%259D%25BE%25E4%25BA%2595%2520%25E7%259F%25B3%25E6%25A0%25B9\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　愛知県出身。陸士卒。陸大卒。陸大在学中に日露戦争に従軍。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　その後、中国に駐在中は、国民党の<a href=\"../p/enseigai.html\">袁世凱</a>打倒に協力。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　いったんは予備役に編入されるも、日中戦争が起こり現役に復帰。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　上海派遣軍司令官、次いで中支那方面軍司令官に就任、首都南京を攻略し復員。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、Ａ級戦犯として<a href=\"../1937/12gyaku.html\">南京大虐殺</a>の責任を問われ、<a href=\"../1948/11tokyo.html\">東京裁判で「絞首刑」の判決</a>。<a href=\"../1948/12senpa.html\">刑死</a>。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
